<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>٥٧٤٠ - حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/556">إِسْحَاقُ بْنُ نَصْرٍ: </a>حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/3447">عَبْدُ الرَّزَّاقِ، </a>عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/6279">مَعْمَرٍ، </a>عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/6737">هَمَّامٍ، </a>عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/3320">أَبِي هُرَيْرَةَ </a><span class="special">﵁</span>،<span class="c5"> عَنِ النَّبِيِّ <span class="special">ﷺ</span> قَالَ:</span> <span class="c2">«الْعَيْنُ حَقٌّ. وَنَهَى عَنِ الْوَشْمِ.»</span><a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>